creator: NaturalCycles AG
descriptionHtml:
Get started with Natural Cycles - the only digital contraceptive CE-marked in Europe as a medical device - and take control of your reproductive health.

Natural Cycles is 93% effective with typical use, and 98% effective with perfect use. The clinical study that determined Natural Cycles' effectiveness is one of the largest of its kind, with 15,000 women and 600,000 menstrual cycles. It was peer reviewed and published in the renowned journal Contraception.*

For added context, the pill is 91% effective with typical use and >99% with perfect use, and the IUD is one of the most effective form of birth control, with both typical and perfect use >99%. That said, there is no 'one size fits all' and the choice of contraception varies from woman to woman.

What you get with Natural Cycles:
○ Effective and hormone-free contraception
○ Daily updates on where you are in your cycle
○ When you are in the fertile phase of your cycle and need to use protection (e.g. condoms)
○ When your ovulation is detected and predicted
○ When your period is coming up and when you can expect PMS
○ The science behind your menstrual cycle

Natural Cycles is:
○ The first and only contraceptive app available in both the USA and Europe
○ Backed by years of scientific research
○ CE marked & FDA cleared

Pricing Plans:
Yearly Plan (Recommended): 49.99 GBP/year. Free thermometer.
Monthly Plan: 6.99 GBP/ month. Thermometer not included.

Precautions:
○ Natural Cycles’ effectiveness as a contraceptive is not affected by fluctuating temperatures and/or irregular cycles (i.e. cycles shorter than 21 days or longer than 35 days). However, you will experience an increased number of red days as predicting fertility is more difficult in these circumstances.
○ Natural Cycles does not protect against sexually transmitted infections (STIs). Use a condom to protect against STIs.

Want to learn more about Natural Cycles?


► Visit the Natural Cycles website
► Instagram
► Facebook

► Privacy Policy

To use Natural Cycles, you need to understand English or one of the supported languages.

* E. Berglund Scherwitzl et al. Perfect-use and typical-use Pearl Index of a contraceptive mobile app. Find the article here

Natural Cycles is 93% effective with typical use, and 98% effective with perfect use. The clinical study that determined Natural Cycles' effectiveness is one of the largest of its kind, with 15,000 women and 600,000 menstrual cycles. It was peer reviewed and published in the renowned journal Contraception.*

For added context, the pill is 91% effective with typical use and >99% with perfect use, and the IUD is one of the most effective form of birth control, with both typical and perfect use >99%. That said, there is no 'one size fits all' and the choice of contraception varies from woman to woman.

What you get with Natural Cycles:
○ Effective and hormone-free contraception
○ Daily updates on where you are in your cycle
○ When you are in the fertile phase of your cycle and need to use protection (e.g. condoms)
○ When your ovulation is detected and predicted
○ When your period is coming up and when you can expect PMS
○ The science behind your menstrual cycle

Natural Cycles is:
○ The first and only contraceptive app available in both the USA and Europe
○ Backed by years of scientific research
○ CE marked & FDA cleared

Pricing Plans:
Yearly Plan (Recommended): 49.99 GBP/year. Free thermometer.
Monthly Plan: 6.99 GBP/ month. Thermometer not included.

Precautions:
○ Natural Cycles’ effectiveness as a contraceptive is not affected by fluctuating temperatures and/or irregular cycles (i.e. cycles shorter than 21 days or longer than 35 days). However, you will experience an increased number of red days as predicting fertility is more difficult in these circumstances.
○ Natural Cycles does not protect against sexually transmitted infections (STIs). Use a condom to protect against STIs.

Want to learn more about Natural Cycles?

► Facebook

To use Natural Cycles, you need to understand English or one of the supported languages.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
There are many exciting updates in this new app version:

○ we have added more types of sex to our sex log feature so you can better keep track of how/if your sexual activity changes throughout your cycle
○ in order to enable you to discover how skin evolves throughout your cycle, we have developed a new tracker that helps you log your skin changes
○ we have added new features for users coming off hormonal birth control

Enjoy all of these and more!

title: Natural Cycles - Birth Control

creator: NaturalCycles AG
descriptionHtml:
Choose Natural Cycles - the only birth control app that is cleared by the FDA in the US and CE-marked in Europe as a medical device - and take birth control into your own hands.

Particle physicist Dr. Elina Berglund initially developed Natural Cycles to offer women an effective, non-hormonal method of birth control. The app identifies ovulation by analyzing basal body temperature, letting you know when you're fertile and when you’re not. Natural Cycles is different from fertility and period trackers, as it is a clinically proven birth control option, alongside the pill, IUD and the condom.

What you get with Natural Cycles


○ Effectiveness - the app is FDA-cleared in the US and CE-marked in Europe
○ Knowledge of when you're fertile and when you're not
○ Reliable ovulation detection and predictions
○ Personal insights around your cycle, enabled by our proprietary algorithm
○ Useful notifications including PMS alerts and when your period is due

Birth control effectiveness


Natural Cycles is 93% effective with typical use, and 98% effective with perfect use. The clinical study that determined Natural Cycles' effectiveness is one of the largest of its kind, with 15,000 women and 600,000 menstrual cycles. It was peer reviewed and published in the renowned journal Contraception.*

For added context, the pill is 91% effective with typical use and >99% with perfect use, and the IUD is one of the most effective form of birth control, with both typical and perfect use >99%. That said, there is no 'one size fits all' and the choice of birth control is very individual from woman to woman.

Our Story


Natural Cycles was founded by the couple Dr. Elina Berglund and Dr. Raoul Scherwitzl, who wanted an effective method of birth control that was hormone-free and non-invasive. As a former member of the European Organisation for Nuclear Research (CERN), Elina was part of the team that discovered the Higgs Boson particle – one of the most significant discoveries in particle physics, that went on to win a Nobel Prize.

Using the techniques she had learned through the Higgs Boson project, Elina created an algorithm to analyze temperature readings, taking factors like sperm survival, temperature fluctuations, variations in cycle length, ovulation day, and the length of the follicular and luteal phase into account to identify fertile and non-fertile days. Raoul suggested that they would turn the fertility algorithm into an app, to allow other couples to benefit from their innovation. Natural Cycles was born.

Pricing plans


○ Yearly plan: $89.99/year.
○ Monthly plan: $9.99/month.
○ A subscription is needed to use the app. A free demo mode is available.

Precautions


○ Natural Cycles does not protect against sexually transmitted infections (STIs). Use a condom to protect against STIs.
○ No method of birth control is 100% effective, even when using the birth control app perfectly you can still have an unintended pregnancy.
○ Natural Cycles is for women over the age of 18.
○ Natural Cycles is only available as a method of birth control in the US and in Europe.
○ To use Natural Cycles, you need to understand English or one of the supported languages.

Before you start using Natural Cycles, read the User Manual, Terms of Use and Privacy Policy.
► User Manual
► Terms of Use
► Privacy Policy

*E. Berglund Scherwitzl et al. “Perfect-use and typical-use Pearl Index of a contraceptive mobile app”, Contraception, Volume 96, Issue 6, 420 - 425.

Get started with Natural Cycles - the only digital contraceptive CE-marked in Europe as a medical device - and take control of your reproductive health.

Natural Cycles is 93% effective with typical use, and 98% effective with perfect use. The clinical study that determined Natural Cycles' effectiveness is one of the largest of its kind, with 15,000 women and 600,000 menstrual cycles. It was peer reviewed and published in the renowned journal Contraception.*

For added context, the pill is 91% effective with typical use and >99% with perfect use, and the IUD is one of the most effective form of birth control, with both typical and perfect use >99%. That said, there is no 'one size fits all' and the choice of contraception varies from woman to woman.

What you get with Natural Cycles:
○ Effective and hormone-free contraception
○ Daily updates on where you are in your cycle
○ When you are in the fertile phase of your cycle and need to use protection (e.g. condoms)
○ When your ovulation is detected and predicted
○ When your period is coming up and when you can expect PMS
○ The science behind your menstrual cycle

Natural Cycles is:
○ The first and only contraceptive app available in both the USA and Europe
○ Backed by years of scientific research
○ CE marked & FDA cleared

Pricing Plans:
Yearly Plan (Recommended): 49.99 GBP/year. Free thermometer.
Monthly Plan: 6.99 GBP/ month. Thermometer not included.

Precautions:
○ Natural Cycles’ effectiveness as a contraceptive is not affected by fluctuating temperatures and/or irregular cycles (i.e. cycles shorter than 21 days or longer than 35 days). However, you will experience an increased number of red days as predicting fertility is more difficult in these circumstances.
○ Natural Cycles does not protect against sexually transmitted infections (STIs). Use a condom to protect against STIs.

Want to learn more about Natural Cycles?


► Visit the Natural Cycles website
► Instagram
► Facebook

Before you start using Natural Cycles, read the User Manual, Terms of Use and Privacy Policy.
► User Manual
► Terms of Use
► Privacy Policy

To use Natural Cycles, you need to understand English or one of the supported languages.

* E. Berglund Scherwitzl et al. Perfect-use and typical-use Pearl Index of a contraceptive mobile app. Find the article here

title: Natural Cycles - Contraception

creator: NaturalCycles AG
descriptionHtml:
NC° Birth Control · NC° Plan Pregnancy

○ NEW: Natural Cycles° is working with smart ring innovators, ŌURA, to create a seamless experience for those looking to plan or prevent pregnancy naturally
○ The #1 Rated Birth Control and Ovulation Temperature Tracker App in the US
○ Subscription-based to protect your data. We will never sell your personal data.
○ The only birth control app cleared by the FDA as a regulated medical device
○ Adaptive technology that uses your unique cycle and basal temperature to track ovulation so you know exactly when you're fertile, and what days you can and cannot get pregnant
○ Daily insights into your fertility and personal ovulatory pattern to help with your birth control or natural family planning needs
○ Scientifically proven to be effective: 93% effective with typical use, and 98% effective with perfect use
○ Switch modes and use to plan a pregnancy. Great for couples to follow ovulation and trying to conceive

Natural Cycles is not just a period or basal body temperature tracker. Most other fertility tracking apps assume your cycle is 28 days long. This means the fertile window they give you is not tailored to you. Our algorithm significantly reduces the risk of you being assigned an incorrect fertile day as it uses your personal data. This reduces the risk of unwanted pregnancy, or can help you plan pregnancy and conceive with greater precision.

Pricing Plans


○ Yearly Plan (Recommended): $99.99/year.
○ Monthly Plan: $12.99/month.
○ A subscription is needed to use the app; Natural Cycles is intended for long-term use.
○ We charge a subscription in order to protect you and your data. Free apps need to make money, so many of them do so by sharing or selling their users’ data to third parties for advertising. We will never sell your data because our users' privacy is paramount to us.


Precautions


○ Natural Cycles does not protect against sexually transmitted infections (STIs). Use a condom to protect against STIs.
○ No method of birth control is 100% effective, even when using the birth control app perfectly you can still have an unintended pregnancy.
○ Natural Cycles is for women over the age of 18.
○ Natural Cycles is only available as a method of birth control in the US and in Europe.
○ To use Natural Cycles, you need to understand English or one of the supported languages.

Looking for a reliable fertility app to get pregnant? Natural Cycles is a perfect period and ovulation tracker app that will meet your needs.

Before you start using Natural Cycles for birth control, fertility and/or ovulation tracker, read the User Manual, Terms of Use and Privacy Policy.
► User Manual
► Terms of Use
► Privacy Policy

*E. Berglund Scherwitzl et al. “Perfect-use and typical-use Pearl Index of a contraceptive mobile app”, Contraception, Volume 96, Issue 6, 420 - 425.

title: Natural Cycles - Contraception

creator: NaturalCycles AG
descriptionHtml:
Natural Cycles: The first FDA Cleared birth control app. Supporting 2.5M women over 10 years.

100% hormone free. No prescription is needed. Scientifically proven to be 93% effective with typical use and 98% effective with perfect use.

WHY NATURAL CYCLES?
Natural Cycles is your life-long fertility partner. You can use the app for birth control, pregnancy planning, tracking your period, and more.

By utilizing our cutting-edge basal body temperature tracker, you can view your personalized fertile windows and ovulation periods.

PROVEN & TRUSTED
● Trusted by over 2.5M women
● Trusted for natural family planning
● #1 birth control and ovulation temperature tracker in the US FDA cleared Best Birth Control app by Healthline and Bestapp.com

HIGHLIGHTS
Natural Cycles is your all-in-one fertility partner – for birth control, planning a pregnancy, and everything in-between:
● Personalized period calendar & cycle tracker
● 100% hormone-free
● ŌURA Ring compatible
● Monitor your body & baby throughout pregnancy
● Track your mood, sex drive, PMS & pain
● Receive daily insights into fertility and ovulation patterns
● Multiple languages supported: English, Spanish, Swedish, and more ● Cutting-edge adaptive technology
● Private & secure

HOW IT WORKS
Using a period tracking app? You may be receiving inaccurate information about your body.

The majority of those apps assume everyone has the same cycle length & fertile window. While research shows that only 13% of women have a 28-day cycle.

Natural Cycles determines your fertility status based on your unique body temperature and cycle. It even works with irregular cycles.
All you need to do is add your temperature, and let the app do the work.
4. Measure your temperature and add it to the app
5. Wait for the algorithm to calculate your fertility
6. Check your fertility to prevent or plan pregnancy naturally

Learn the unique pattern of your cycle & fertility with tailored insights to help with your birth control, period tracking, natural family planning needs, and everything in-between.

INVEST IN YOUR JOURNEY
We are committed to protecting our Cyclers’ data. Many free period tracking and birth control apps make money by selling their users’ data.

We never sell or share data because our pricing is upfront:
● Year: £59.99 (free thermometer)
● Monthly: £8.99 per month (not including thermometer - £10)
We’re dedicated to providing our Cyclers with a private long term solution they can trust through different stages of their life.

DISCLAIMERS
● Natural Cycles does not prevent sexually transmitted infections
● Natural Cycles is for women over the age of 18

100% hormone free. No prescription is needed. Scientifically proven to be 93% effective with typical use and 98% effective with perfect use.

WHY NATURAL CYCLES?
Natural Cycles is your life-long fertility partner. You can use the app for birth control, pregnancy planning, tracking your period, and more.

By utilizing our cutting-edge basal body temperature tracker, you can view your personalized fertile windows and ovulation periods.

PROVEN & TRUSTED
● Trusted by over 2.5M women
● Trusted for natural family planning
● #1 birth control and ovulation temperature tracker in the US FDA cleared Best Birth Control app by Healthline and Bestapp.com

HIGHLIGHTS
Natural Cycles is your all-in-one fertility partner – for birth control, planning a pregnancy, and everything in-between:
● Measure your temperature using your Oura Ring, NC° Bluetooth thermometer, or Apple Watch.
● Personalized period calendar & cycle tracker
● 100% hormone-free
● Monitor your body & baby throughout pregnancy
● Track your mood, sex drive, PMS & pain
● Receive daily insights into fertility and ovulation patterns
● Multiple languages supported: English, Spanish, Swedish, and more ● Cutting-edge adaptive technology
● Private & secure

HOW IT WORKS
Using a period tracking app? You may be receiving inaccurate information about your body.

The majority of those apps assume everyone has the same cycle length & fertile window. While research shows that only 13% of women have a 28-day cycle.

Natural Cycles determines your fertility status based on your unique body temperature and cycle. It even works with irregular cycles.
All you need to do is add your temperature, and let the app do the work.
4. Measure your temperature and add it to the app
5. Wait for the algorithm to calculate your fertility
6. Check your fertility to prevent or plan pregnancy naturally

Learn the unique pattern of your cycle & fertility with tailored insights to help with your birth control, period tracking, natural family planning needs, and everything in-between.

INVEST IN YOUR JOURNEY
We are committed to protecting our Cyclers’ data. Many free period tracking and birth control apps make money by selling their users’ data.

We never sell or share data because our pricing is upfront:
● Year: £69.99 (free thermometer)
● Monthly: £9.99 per month
We’re dedicated to providing our Cyclers with a private long term solution they can trust through different stages of their life.

DISCLAIMERS
● Natural Cycles does not prevent sexually transmitted infections
● Natural Cycles is for women over the age of 18
descriptionShort: The only CE-marked digital fertility & ovulation tracker for birth control

title:
Natural Cycles - Birth Control
5.1.11

creator: NaturalCycles AG
descriptionHtml: 👩🏽‍🤝‍👩🏼Trusted by 3M+ women over 10 years. 🏆 Awarded Best Birth Control app by Healthline and Bestapp.com 🏆 100% hormone-free contraception. No prescription is needed. Scientifically proven to be 93% effective with typical use and 98% effective with perfect use.HIGHLIGHTS: ● The NC° app uses your body temperature to track ovulation so you know exactly when you're fertile – and what days you can/cannot get pregnant. ● The NC° app adapts to your unique cycle, even if it’s irregular. ● No hormones, no side effects, no pills or procedures – consider birth control revolutionized. ● Scientifically proven to be effective: 93% effective with typical use, and 98% effective with perfect use. ● Sign up to NC° Annual subscription for a FREE thermometer, and start measuring today! ● Offers advanced data protection – Natural Cycles will never sell your data. ● Get daily fertility insights + personal ovulatory patterns to help with your natural family planning needs. ● The NC° app features customizable mood trackers, great for getting to know your body better. ● Measure your temperature by wearing an Oura Ring or Apple Watch Series 8 or newer (while you sleep), or with the NC° Thermometer (in the morning). ● Get reimbursed for your NC° subscription – US users are now covered by insurance. WHY NATURAL CYCLES? Natural Cycles is more than a period tracker. Most other fertility tracking apps assume your cycle is 28 days long, even though 87% of women have cycle lengths that don't fit into the 28 day pattern.. We understand that birth control is not a one-size-fits-all. Your cycle is unique to you! Our algorithm uses personalized temperature data to confirm your ovulation, reducing the risk of you being assigned an incorrect fertile day. Unlike period trackers, the NC° app allows you to identify your fertility status daily, so you can prevent pregnancy or plan for it with greater precision. From birth control to planning pregnancy and every cycle in between – Natural Cycles is there for you with each stage of your fertility journey. Still not sure? Download the app and test out our Demo Mode. The app supports syncing with Apple Health. *E. Berglund Scherwitzl et al. “Perfect-use and typical-use Pearl Index of a contraceptive mobile app”, Contraception, Volume 96, Issue 6, 420 - 425. PRICING PLANS: ● Annual subscription (and FREE NC° Thermometer): £69.99/year ● Monthly subscription: £9.99/month ● We recommend a minimum of 2-3 cycles to get the most out of your Natural Cycles subscription. ● Our subscription fee helps to protect you and your data. Many free apps work by selling their users’ data to third parties for advertising. Privacy is non-negotiable for us; we will never sell your data. PRECAUTIONS: ● Natural Cycles does not protect against sexually transmitted infections (STIs). Use a condom to protect against STIs. ● No method of contraception is 100% effective. Even when using the birth control app perfectly, there is still a chance of getting pregnant. ● Natural Cycles is for women over the age of 18. ● Natural Cycles is only available as a method of birth control in the US and in Europe. ● To use Natural Cycles, you need to understand English or one of the supported languages.

descriptionHtml: 👩🏽‍🤝‍👩🏼Trusted by 3M+ women over 10 years. 🏆 Awarded Best Birth Control app by Healthline and Bestapp.com 🏆 100% hormone-free contraception. No prescription is needed. Scientifically proven to be 93% effective with typical use and 98% effective with perfect use.HIGHLIGHTS: ● The NC° app uses your body temperature to track ovulation so you know exactly when you're fertile – and what days you can/cannot get pregnant. ● The NC° app adapts to your unique cycle, even if it’s irregular. ● No hormones, no side effects, no pills or procedures – consider birth control revolutionized. ● Scientifically proven to be effective: 93% effective with typical use, and 98% effective with perfect use. ● Sign up to NC° Annual subscription for a FREE thermometer, and start measuring today! ● Offers advanced data protection – Natural Cycles will never sell your data. ● Get daily fertility insights + personal ovulatory patterns to help with your natural family planning needs. ● The NC° app features customizable mood trackers, great for getting to know your body better. ● Measure your temperature by wearing an Oura Ring or Apple Watch Series 8 or newer (while you sleep), or with the NC° Thermometer (in the morning). ● Get reimbursed for your NC° subscription – US users are now covered by insurance. WHY NATURAL CYCLES? Natural Cycles is more than a period tracker. Most other fertility tracking apps assume your cycle is 28 days long, even though 87% of women have cycle lengths that don't fit into the 28 day pattern.. We understand that birth control is not a one-size-fits-all. Your cycle is unique to you! Our algorithm uses personalized temperature data to confirm your ovulation, reducing the risk of you being assigned an incorrect fertile day. Unlike period trackers, the NC° app allows you to identify your fertility status daily, so you can prevent pregnancy or plan for it with greater precision. From birth control to planning pregnancy and every cycle in between – Natural Cycles is there for you with each stage of your fertility journey. Still not sure? Download the app and test out our Demo Mode. The app supports syncing with Apple Health. *E. Berglund Scherwitzl et al. “Perfect-use and typical-use Pearl Index of a contraceptive mobile app”, Contraception, Volume 96, Issue 6, 420 - 425. PRICING PLANS: ● Annual subscription (and FREE NC° Thermometer): £69.99/year ● Monthly subscription: £9.99/month ● We recommend a minimum of 2-3 cycles to get the most out of your Natural Cycles subscription. ● Our subscription fee helps to protect you and your data. Many free apps work by selling their users’ data to third parties for advertising. Privacy is non-negotiable for us; we will never sell your data. PRECAUTIONS: ● Natural Cycles does not protect against sexually transmitted infections (STIs). Use a condom to protect against STIs. ● No method of contraception is 100% effective. Even when using the birth control app perfectly, there is still a chance of getting pregnant. ● Natural Cycles is for women over the age of 18. ● Natural Cycles is only available as a method of birth control in the US and in Europe. ● To use Natural Cycles, you need to understand English or one of the supported languages.
